data.description: Beautiful custom designed courtyard style home. Everything opens to the large courtyard and pool. Beautiful lake view in the back. This home is in a gated community with "Low" HOA fees which include cable/internet. This community offers a club house, gym, tennis courts and large community pool. "A" Rated Schools! Close to shopping and Vanderbilt Beach is only 5 miles away.  A very unique two story home with 4 bedrooms and 4 full baths. You will love the guest house with full bath and kitchenette. Great for in-laws, guests, kids or home office. A large room with kitchenette and full bath upstairs is furnished as a bedroom with a screened in sitting area. A very comfortable livable home. Heated dipping 14x16  square pool with spa, which leaves room for entertaining in the courtyard. Home has a new roof and is very well maintained. Some furnishings can stay. Owner is down sizing and anxious to negotiate with serious buyer.
